{"tid":2429663,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★騰訊大鑊？人大代表建議規管微信支付手續費","createTime":"2021-03-02T13:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T13:04:02.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"483f3124068c155dac092653a23c00e441643a9a","tid":2429663,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:01:09.000Z","msg":"兩會開幕前夕，內地傳媒報道，全國人大代表、廣東國鼎律師事務所主任朱列玉認為，騰訊控股(00700)旗下流動支付服務微信支付利用其市場優勢，向大部分行業的商戶收取0.6%的手續費及向用戶收取0.1%的提現手續費，違反誠信和公平原則，也不符合公平競爭的市場運作規律，損害了廣大經營者和微信支付服務使用者的合法利益，因此要建議規範微信支付不合理收費行為，大幅度降低微信支付手續費。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210302/bkn-20210302192643362-0302_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20210302%2Fbkn-20210302192643362-0302_00842_001.html&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA%2FUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=15573891\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210302/bkn-20210302192643362-0302_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a022fc50d8d3d4300030a7b1c5f4cf3dc49a2752","tid":2429663,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:01:24.000Z","msg":"割<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70470670a618334606a12d4c8d94e21a628642b6","tid":2429663,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:02:21.000Z","msg":"信用卡收費仲貴，佢唔監管？"},{"pid":"1d077237cf16a73ab59b322c684eb487c276944d","tid":2429663,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:02:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SHmmPBk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSHmmPBk.gif&h=69c43eed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf0